{"tid":570382,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同女友家人親戚打牌會唔會鬆章？","createTime":"2018-02-23T14:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T16:31:17.000Z","uid":36868,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f22ace968023990dc0d647aa6bc9270ba294396d","tid":570382,"uid":36868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"話說女友帶我去同佢地啲親戚食飯<br />\n點知佢衰多口話我鐘意打牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢啲親戚就夾硬拉我去打<br />\n其實我都係鐘意同朋友細細地玩下<br />\n志在思考個過程<br />\n佢啲親戚打到鬼死咁大 又下下做大牌 我又唔想輸錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咪打防守牌同食5番<br />\n到最後扣牌扣到佢地唔打 成餐飯黑哂面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 老鳳輸錢比你架咩 贏你你又唔順氣 真係吹撚漲<br />\n咁多位巴打有冇遇過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df41c18a7bfff78938324e03416fbd4a969f0214","tid":570382,"uid":41509,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"決戰四方城，上場無父子，讓你老尾臭"},{"pid":"b97c26fadc7b997a265343c79063ded920360995","tid":570382,"uid":31542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:57:19.000Z","msg":"打牌係咁打嫁啦 下下出統比你清一色好唔撚好<br />\n咁同佢地講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32842536ddfc72f5c3e4a725ef74befd32dcc1ed","tid":570382,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"私底下問佢拎返啲錢"},{"pid":"16a380e72b9ee032953f28b5103b9a5501f5605b","tid":570382,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"你有技術既話食佢爆棚<br />\n唔係食d垃圾5番<br />\n辣殺"},{"pid":"844a49bb2aa9028479af3b30f562dd4a838bb132","tid":570382,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"你姓吳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff9cafeda7e837e27d46d355ce2d43f97dceda1","tid":570382,"uid":5044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線老馮俾你食糊㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年新年同親戚打牌<br />\n除咗有時贏得太勁鬆少少張<br />\n其他時間一定係絕不鬆手啦 我啲錢唔係錢呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a65cf60e9676d9caf9bf8082d0acac00cba179","tid":570382,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"奶奶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942d6627781847aad5ec1fdcbb471ff909e30c7","tid":570382,"uid":8883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"同佢地講：正花都摸埋你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494bbd6897cd7cdddfcf2cce03d6940e4003600c","tid":570382,"uid":106967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶奶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你要咩我打咩叫做誅"},{"pid":"8f797fbaca4d8445fc58d9825ad64e31107fc40a","tid":570382,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"打幾大先<br />\n佢老豆老母阿婆咪鬆下一兩鋪囉 其他親戚不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a258fb92e9eb902c339941c3a7d4122e4f7dcb8","tid":570382,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"輸左千幾蚊 嗚嗚嗚"},{"pid":"1c8fc47a737b9924197607aa93cfe278f7e0bec9","tid":570382,"uid":164351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"同佢地講：我&quot;鬆&quot;比你呀吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09d533a9e74498815c0deb59bc525a45d3b9de1","tid":570382,"uid":162539,"like":0,"